# Jiggon Algorithm: Momentum Scalper
# A highly aggressive algorithm that buys into rapid volatility spikes.
# It requires the market trend to be heavily defined, and RSI to be pushing extremes
# without waiting for a reversal.

IF RSI > 60 AND MACD > 0.5 AND EMA_TREND == BULLISH THEN BUY
IF RSI < 40 AND MACD < -0.5 AND EMA_TREND == BEARISH THEN SELL
